    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Shrines or small chapels dedicated to a hero, demigod, or person of great dignity; may or may not be located over a grave.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
